```

**Why `onnx-community/Florence-2-base-ft`:** Florence-2 is already listed in `MODEL_FOR_IMAGE_TEXT_TO_TEXT_MAPPING_NAMES` in `models.js`, is well-supported in Transformers.js, and has ONNX weights available under `onnx-community`.

